---
title: Spiced Chicken Dosa Pancake with Sweet Mango Chutney and Mint Raita
description: A dosa is a thin, crêpe-like pancakes traditionally served in India. It is made with besan (also known as gram or chickpea flour), which makes it naturally gluten-free! We're serving it with delicious spiced-chicken, and a cooling mint raita on the side!
